e context-dependence of herbivore top-down effects. Heterogeneity in abiotic and biotic conditions may, therefore, have an important influence on the strength of top-down effects and the role that herbivores play in natural ecosystems. © 2010 The Authors. Journal compilation © 2010 British Ecological Society.},
   author = {Dries P.J. Kuijper and Joris P.G.M. Cromsigt and Bogumiła Jedrzejewska and Stanisław Miścicki and Marcin Churski and Włodzimierz Jedrzejewski and Iwona Kweczlich},
